<Page
  xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
  xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
  xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
  xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
  mc:Ignorable="d"
  d:DesignWidth="1920"
  d:DesignHeight="1080">
  <Viewbox>
    <Grid>
      <Border HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Width="900" Height="1272" Padding="45" 
        TextElement.FontFamily="Times New Roman" TextElement.Foreground="Black" TextElement.FontSize="16" Background="#FFFAEBD7">
        <Border.RenderTransform>
          <TransformGroup>
            <RotateTransform Angle="12" CenterX="432" CenterY="560"/>
            <TranslateTransform X="375"/>
          </TransformGroup>
        </Border.RenderTransform>
        <Border.Effect>
          <DropShadowEffect />
        </Border.Effect>
        <Grid>
		  <Grid.RowDefinitions>
		    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
		    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
		    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
		    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
		    <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
		  </Grid.RowDefinitions>
          <Grid Grid.Row="0" Margin="-40,-45,-40,0">
            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
            <Image Source="{Binding Assets[07_ru_newspaper_header]}" VerticalAlignment="Top" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Width="800" Margin="40,40,40,0"/>
            <!--<Rectangle Grid.ColumnSpan="2" Fill="#FF0000DD" Height="10" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Margin="0,0,0,20" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Width="670"/>
            <Rectangle Grid.ColumnSpan="2" HorizontalAlignment="Right" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Fill="#FF0000FF" Height="10" Width="100" Margin="0,0,0,20"/>-->
          </Grid>
          <TextBlock Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,15">
			№ 35 <Run FontSize="20" Text="•"/> May <Run FontSize="20" Text="•"/> 1988
		  </TextBlock>
          <Image Grid.Row="2" Source="{Binding Assets[07_delta_3_surface_launch_2]}"/>
          <Grid Grid.Row="3" Margin="0,10,0,20">
            <TextBlock Text="Successful test launch of mighty Weapons" TextWrapping="Wrap" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold"/>
			<TextBlock Text="&#1060;&#1086;&#1090;&#1086; &#1042;. &#1044;&#1052;&#1048;&#1058;&#1056;&#1070;&#1050;" TextWrapping="Wrap" HorizontalAlignment="Right" VerticalAlignment="Top" FontWeight="Light"/>
          </Grid>
          <Grid Grid.Row="4" Background="#FFFAEBD7">
            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
			<Grid>
			  <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
			  </Grid.RowDefinitions>
			  <TextBlock Grid.Row="0" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Center" FontSize="36" Text="Mighty Soviet Engineering" Margin="0,0,0,45" />
			  <TextBlock Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Justify" Margin="20,0,10,30">
				The Soviet Union continues to strengthen its position as the vanguard of scientific and technological progress with the successful development and deployment of a new
			  </TextBlock>
			</Grid>
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Column="1" TextAlignment="Justify" Margin="10,30,10,30">
			intercontinental ballistic missile. This latest triumph of socialist engineering stands as a testament to the unwavering dedication of Soviet scientists and workers in the defense of the Motherland.
			<LineBreak/>
			<LineBreak/>
			Designed by the finest minds of the Soviet military-industrial complex, the weapon represents a significant advancement in missile technology,
			</TextBlock>
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Column="2" TextAlignment="Justify" Margin="10,30,20,30">
			boasting enhanced range, precision, and payload capacity. Capable of delivering multiple independently targeted warheads, this formidable weapon ensures the strategic balance necessary to deter imperialist aggression.
			<LineBreak/>
			<LineBreak/>
			 The Minister of Defense lauded the achievement, stating: “this is an unparalleled feat of ingenuity."
			</TextBlock>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Border>
      <Border HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Width="900" Height="1272" Padding="45" 
        TextElement.FontFamily="Times New Roman" TextElement.Foreground="Black" TextElement.FontSize="16" Background="#FFFAEBD7">
        <Border.RenderTransform>
          <TransformGroup>
            <RotateTransform Angle="-6" CenterX="432" CenterY="560"/>
            <TranslateTransform X="-313"/>
          </TransformGroup>
        </Border.RenderTransform>
        <Border.Effect>
          <DropShadowEffect />
        </Border.Effect>
        <Grid>
		  <Grid.RowDefinitions>
		    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
		    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
		    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
		    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
		    <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
		  </Grid.RowDefinitions>
          <Grid Grid.Row="0" Margin="-40,-45,-40,0">
            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
            <Image Source="{Binding Assets[07_ru_newspaper_header]}" VerticalAlignment="Top" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Width="800" Margin="40,35,40,0"/>
            <!--<TextBlock Text="Правдоруб" Grid.Column="1" FontSize="135" FontFamily="Yu Gothic UI" FontWeight="Bold"/>
            <Rectangle Grid.ColumnSpan="2" Fill="#FF0000DD" Height="10" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Margin="40,0,0,20" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Width="300"/>
            <Rectangle Grid.ColumnSpan="2" HorizontalAlignment="Right" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Fill="#FF0000FF" Height="10" Width="100" Margin="0,0,40,20"/>-->
          </Grid>
          <TextBlock Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,15">
№ 34 <Run FontSize="20" Text="•"/> May <Run FontSize="20" Text="•"/> 1988
		  </TextBlock>
          <Image Grid.Row="2" Source="{Binding Assets[07_ticonderoga]}"/>
          <Grid Grid.Row="3" Margin="0,10,0,20">
            <TextBlock Text="Aggressive imperialist vessels menace our ships, often passing close to examine us" TextWrapping="Wrap" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold"/>
			<TextBlock Text="&#x420;&#x438;&#x441;&#x443;&#x43D;&#x43E;&#x43A; &#x412;. &#x414;&#x41C;&#x418;&#x422;&#x420;&#x42E;&#x41A;" TextWrapping="Wrap" HorizontalAlignment="Right" VerticalAlignment="Top" FontWeight="Light"/>
          </Grid>
          <Grid Grid.Row="4" Background="#FFFAEBD7">
            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
              <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
			<Grid>
			  <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
			  </Grid.RowDefinitions>
			  <TextBlock Grid.Row="0" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Center" FontSize="36" Text="Imperialist Aggression" Margin="0,0,0,45" />
			  <TextBlock Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Justify" Margin="20,0,10,30">
			Today, the world bears witness to the treacherous and unprovoked assault of the imperialist Western powers against the peace-loving peoples of the Soviet Union and its socialist allies. In the early hours of the morning, NATO forces launched a series of aggressive military actions against the Naval Forces of the Warsaw Pact, violating international law and revealing their true, warmongering nature.
			<LineBreak/>
			Despite decades of Soviet efforts to preserve peace and stability, the imperialist bloc, driven by insatiable greed and fear of socialist progress,
			  </TextBlock>
			</Grid>
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Column="1" TextAlignment="Justify" Margin="10,36,10,30">
			has chosen the path of war. Under the guise of so-called ‘scientific data gathering’ NATO forces have engaged in blatant provocations along the Northern Coast. Military vessels, adorned with the insignia of American and British aggressors, have violated socialist waters, and attacked our impressive Rocket Forces.
			<LineBreak/>
			The General Secretary, in an emergency session of the Politburo, condemned the imperialist actions, declaring that the Soviet people will not waver in the defense of their homeland. “The enemy has revealed its hand, but they will soon learn that the Soviet Union and its socialist allies will never be broken. Our military Comrades will ensure our victory.”
			</TextBlock>
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Column="2" TextAlignment="Justify" Margin="10,36,20,30">
			Reports from the front indicate that our brave forces have already engaged the aggressors, dealing significant blows to their Naval Forces. In the skies, heroic Soviet pilots have demonstrated the superiority of socialist naval aviation and in the seas our superlative submarine forces will soon show their value.
			<LineBreak/>
			The people of the Soviet Union stand united in this moment of trial. In every factory, workers redouble their efforts to supply our valiant defenders with the necessary tools of victory. In every city and village, citizens rally behind the banner of Lenin, prepared to sacrifice all in the defense of socialism. 
			</TextBlock>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
		</Border>
    </Grid>
  </Viewbox>
</Page>